---
// Why Revival section - Conor's differentiators and credibility
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm-white" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-sage font-medium mb-3 reveal">Why Revival Recovery</p>
      <h2 id="why-heading" class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-navy mb-6 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        A Provider Who Truly Understands
      </h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-lg leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-2">
        Conor Westerman brings more than clinical expertise—he brings lived experience, deep empathy, and a genuine commitment to your recovery.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Photo Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 reveal-left">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-sage/20 to-amber/10 rounded-2xl transform -rotate-2"></div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-cream">
            <!-- Dog photo - mobile only -->
            <img
              src="/images/conor-headshot.jpg"
              alt="Conor Westerman, PMHNP-BC"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover lg:hidden"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <!-- Headshot - desktop only -->
            <img
              src="/images/conor-headshot-2.jpg"
              alt="Conor Westerman, PMHNP-BC"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hidden lg:block"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Credentials overlay -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-4 right-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-display text-xl text-navy">Conor Westerman</p>
              <p class="text-sage font-medium">PMHNP-BC</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-8">
        <!-- Differentiator 1 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-sage/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-navy mb-2">13+ Years in Personal Recovery</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
                Conor doesn't just understand addiction from textbooks—he's lived it and overcome it. This personal journey gives him unique insight into what truly helps people heal and stay well.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Differentiator 2 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-sage/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-navy mb-2">Decade of Mental Health Experience</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
                Over 10 years working in mental health settings, including extensive experience at The Meadows Behavioral Healthcare—one of the nation's most respected treatment centers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Differentiator 3 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-sage/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-navy mb-2">Board-Certified Expertise</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
                PMHNP-BC certified with specialized training in trauma-informed care, evidence-based practices, and the latest psychiatric treatments including medication-assisted therapy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Differentiator 4 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-sage/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-navy mb-2">Whole-Person Approach</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
                True healing addresses mind, body, and spirit. Conor's approach combines clinical excellence with genuine compassion, meeting you where you are on your journey.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="pt-4 reveal">
          <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sage hover:text-sage-dark font-medium transition-colors">
            Learn More About Conor
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
